name: Mike Mintz
text: Good food fair priced and quick service

name: Ashlee Minyard
text: My favorite thing to order here is a toasted Club sandwich with extra garlic butter on the bread, without the Italian dressing (ham, bacon, turkey, and mozzarella cheese) with Ranch dressing to dip it in. Their chicken, bacon, and ranch sandwiches are pretty good too, but the Club with Ranch is by far my favorite.

name: Leo Lotspeich
text: The pizza is always awesome and the calzones are too. It's a bit greasy at times, but honestly, that's how we prefer it. The parking is a little dismal, but they are rarely ever busy when we visit.

name: king of the underworld and miller of kings
text: Current staff is friendly and food is up to par

name: becky campo
text: Toasted club sandwiches with all the vegetables is what I would recommend
